{
  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Sawa Deewa Maisi tik\nlabbi no tahmi wiſsfwehtakahm/\nkā no tahmi fwehtahim Leetahim\nwarr tas ehft.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tomehr pee ta Breekſch-\nwelkama tam ne buhs nahkt/ un\npee ta Altara ne pee-eet/ tapehz\nka winnam Waina irr/ ka tas\nmannu fwehtu Weetu ne ſagah-\nna/ jo es eſmu tas KUNGS/\ntas tohs fwehti.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Mohsus runnaja to us\nAāronu/ un us winna Dehleem/\nun us wiſſceim Israēta Behrneem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Elz to runnaja tas\nKUNGSusMohsu/un\nfazzija:\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Runna us Aāronu un win-\nna Dehleem/ ka teem buhs no I-\nſraēta Behrnu fwehtahm Lee-\ntahm/ ko tee man fwehti atſtah-\ntecs/ un mannas Swehtibas\nWahrdn ne ſagahniht/ Es eſmu\ntas KUNGS.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Sakki us teem: Wiſſam\nWihrain starp juhsn Pehznah-\nfameem/ kas starp wiſſu juhsō\nDſimmunn pee tahmi fwehtahm\nLeetahm/ to Israēta Behrni tam\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "KUNGAM fwehti/ pee-ees/ tad\nwinna Neſchkibſtiba pahr winnu\nirr/ tas taps isdeldehts no man-\nna Waiga/ Es eſmu tas KUNgs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ne weenam no Aārona\nDſimmuna/ kad tas ſpittaligs\nirr/ jeb kan ta Meeſa pill/ buhs\nno tahmi fwehtahm Leetahim ehft/\nteekams tas fchkihsts tohp/ ir kas\njeb kurru neſchkihstu Meeſu ais-\nkax/ no kahda Mirrona/ jeb kam\ngulloht Sehkla iſpill.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jeb ja kas kahdu leenamu\nTahrpu aiskaxx / no ka tas nei-\nſchkihsts irr/jeb kahdu Zilweſu/no\nka tas neſchkihsts irr / ar jeb kurru\nLeetu tas ſagahnihts tohp.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tas/ kas to irr aiskahris /\nbuhs neſchkihsts lihds Wakkaram/\nun ne ehdihs no tahmi fwehtahm\nLeetahm / bet winnam buhs fa-\nwu Meeſu artthdeni pehrt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Rad ta Saule nogahjuti/\ntad taps tas fchkihsts/ un pehz\nto warr tas no tahmi fwehtahm\nLeetahm ehft/ jo tas irr winna\nBarriba.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Kahdu Maitu/ jeb kas fa-\nplohsſihts irr/ tam ne buhs ehft /\nar to ſagahnidamees/ es eſmu\ntas KUNGS.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Teem tad buhs mannu Pa-\nwehlefchannu turreht/ kateem win-\nnas deht Grehki ne irr janefs/ uu\neektch teem noinirſt/ kad tee win-\nan ſagahnihs / Es eſmu tas\nKUNGS/ kas tohs fwehti.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ne weenam Sweſchinee-\nkam buhs to Swehtu ehft/ weens\nPeedſhwotajs pee kahda Pree-\nſtera/\n"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
  "notes": ""
}
